{"expireTime":9007200815667334000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-ast-6b12daaf25fbdae00fbbc2208b8e6b5f--","val":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":1,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"8個中小企低成本網上宣傳方法","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":2,"offset":1},"end":{"line":1,"column":16,"offset":15},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":17,"offset":16},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"無論是個人品牌、中小企業還是大公司，都需要有良好的市場推廣策略來配合產品服務的銷售，持續性吸引新客戶群。中小企和初創企業往往煩惱於欠缺資金和人力來推廣品牌和產品服務。不過，隨著現今網絡的發展，網上推廣成本更易受控制，以下是8個低成本網上推廣方法，幫助中小企業和初創公司在市場推廣上突圍而出。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":18},"end":{"line":3,"column":146,"offset":163},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":18},"end":{"line":3,"column":146,"offset":163},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"登記Google 我的商家 Google My Business","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":3,"offset":168},"end":{"line":6,"column":35,"offset":200},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":166},"end":{"line":6,"column":37,"offset":202},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"中小企透過登記Google 我的商家，讓自己的公司地址和業務在Google 搜尋引擎和Goggle 地圖上出現，令客戶更容易找到你的公司。","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":204},"end":{"line":8,"column":70,"offset":273},"indent":[]}},{"type":"link","title":"Google My Business","url":"https://www.google.com/business/","children":[{"type":"text","value":"登記Google my business","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":71,"offset":274},"end":{"line":8,"column":91,"offset":294},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":70,"offset":273},"end":{"line":8,"column":147,"offset":350},"indent":[]}},{"type":"text","value":" 無須任何費用，成功登記後公司的資料，例如地址、網站、營業時間、路線圖和電話等會在搜尋時出現在當眼的位置，對增加公司的曝光率大有幫助，成功令公司在同行競爭中突圍而出。Google My Business 還可以增設相片，讓客戶進一步了解公司銷售的產品和店鋪裝潢，展示公司的獨特之處。客戶也可以在你的Google My  Business 上對你公司的服務和產品進行評價，增加口碑。","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":147,"offset":350},"end":{"line":8,"column":337,"offset":540},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":204},"end":{"line":8,"column":337,"offset":540},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"善用社交媒體 Social Media Marketing","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":3,"offset":545},"end":{"line":11,"column":32,"offset":574},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":543},"end":{"line":11,"column":34,"offset":576},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"現時社交媒體大行其道，使用社交媒體來推廣公司品牌和進行銷售已是大勢所趨。社交媒體的用戶人數眾多，根據facebook Ads Manager 和Snapchat Ads Manager 2018年的數據顯示，Facebook 在香港的每月活躍用戶高達540萬，年輕人較多使用的Instagram每月活躍用戶有280萬，而Snatchat 則有51萬本港用戶。其他的社交媒體例如 Twitter、LinkedIn和Google+ 都是中小企可以善用的網上宣傳渠道。懂得善用這些社交媒體，增加與客戶群的網上互動，對提升公司的品牌形象、產品和服務銷售都會無往而不利。","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":577},"end":{"line":12,"column":281,"offset":857},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":577},"end":{"line":12,"column":281,"offset":857},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"網上廣告宣傳 Online Advertisement","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":3,"offset":861},"end":{"line":14,"column":30,"offset":888},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":859},"end":{"line":14,"column":32,"offset":890},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"中小企往往欠缺人力資源和大量資金來推廣告，不能好像大公司花幾百萬請代言人或者落廣告來宣傳公司品牌。網上廣告例如Facebook 和Google 廣告的出現令中小企和初創企業可以更容易控制廣告成本，小至每日幾十元都可以進行網上廣告宣傳。可惜有時facebook 和Google 的廣告效果強差人意，花了錢但見不到效果。最近Google伙伴公司培育計畫的新創公司","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1,"offset":891},"end":{"line":15,"column":180,"offset":1070},"indent":[]}},{"type":"link","title":"goodad.co","url":"https://www.goodad.co/","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Goodad.co","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":181,"offset":1071},"end":{"line":15,"column":190,"offset":1080},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":180,"offset":1070},"end":{"line":15,"column":227,"offset":1117},"indent":[]}},{"type":"text","value":" 推出人工智能的網上廣告平台， 幫助中小企更容易在網上進行廣告宣傳。他們的網上宣傳平台","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":227,"offset":1117},"end":{"line":15,"column":270,"offset":1160},"indent":[]}},{"type":"link","title":"goodad","url":"https://www.goodad.co/","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Goodad","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":271,"offset":1161},"end":{"line":15,"column":277,"offset":1167},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":270,"offset":1160},"end":{"line":15,"column":311,"offset":1201},"indent":[]}},{"type":"text","value":"是一個零佣金的落廣告平台，由本港團隊研發，配合繁簡體關鍵字，讓中小企更易掌握網上廣告的技巧。 即使中小型公司沒有團隊專門負責marketing，都能輕易透過這個平台掌握在Google落廣告的技巧。對本港中小企和初創公司來說，絕對是一大福音。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":311,"offset":1201},"end":{"line":15,"column":431,"offset":1321},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1,"offset":891},"end":{"line":15,"column":431,"offset":1321},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"內容營銷 Content Marketing","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":3,"offset":1325},"end":{"line":17,"column":25,"offset":1347},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1,"offset":1323},"end":{"line":17,"column":27,"offset":1349},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"現時的消費者對於大量的硬性廣告宣傳已經很厭倦，使用內容營銷則能有效地吸引潛在的新客戶，並和現有的客戶群建立長期的關係，提升銷售轉化率。內容營銷是針對客戶的需要和痛點，定期發放有用、有教育性的資訊給這些客戶，為他們解決一些問題或者疑惑，滿足他們的需求，從而提升公司在客戶心目中的品牌價值，提升信任度。內容發放不只限於文字形式，善用短片、廣播(podcast)、網上課程等形式來創立有價值資訊，吸引客戶的注意力。內容營銷是成本低但漫長的推廣策略，需要長時間、持續性地發放有價值的資訊來建立公司的信譽。","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1,"offset":1350},"end":{"line":18,"column":249,"offset":1598},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1,"offset":1350},"end":{"line":18,"column":249,"offset":1598},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"電郵營銷 Email Marketing","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":3,"offset":1602},"end":{"line":20,"column":23,"offset":1622},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1,"offset":1600},"end":{"line":20,"column":25,"offset":1624},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"電郵營銷是中小企另一個低成本市場推廣的方法。當大家都有電郵營銷已死的迷思，其實很多大公司和中小企成功利用電郵營銷來建立客戶關係、推廣公司的產品和服務，及增加客戶對公司的忠誠度。現時有很多發展成熟、易用的電郵營銷工具例如Mailchimp, Active Campaign 或者Converkit, 中小企業可通過這些工具收集客戶的電郵，定期向客戶群發個人化的郵件，與客戶建立長遠的關係，為公司帶來可觀的收入。","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1,"offset":1625},"end":{"line":21,"column":205,"offset":1829},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1,"offset":1625},"end":{"line":21,"column":205,"offset":1829},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建立和完善公司的網站 Built and Optimize Your Website","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":3,"offset":1833},"end":{"line":23,"column":45,"offset":1875},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1,"offset":1831},"end":{"line":23,"column":47,"offset":1877},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"隨著科技的進步，現時建立一個網站已經不是什麼難事。很多免費網站創建平台例如","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1,"offset":1878},"end":{"line":24,"column":38,"offset":1915},"indent":[]}},{"type":"link","title":"wix","url":"https://www.wix.com/","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wix","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":39,"offset":1916},"end":{"line":24,"column":42,"offset":1919},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":38,"offset":1915},"end":{"line":24,"column":71,"offset":1948},"indent":[]}},{"type":"text","value":", ","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":71,"offset":1948},"end":{"line":24,"column":73,"offset":1950},"indent":[]}},{"type":"link","title":"weebly","url":"https://www.weebly.com/hk","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Weebly","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":74,"offset":1951},"end":{"line":24,"column":80,"offset":1957},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":73,"offset":1950},"end":{"line":24,"column":117,"offset":1994},"indent":[]}},{"type":"text","value":" 和","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":117,"offset":1994},"end":{"line":24,"column":119,"offset":1996},"indent":[]}},{"type":"link","title":"webflow","url":"https://webflow.com/","children":[{"type":"text","value":"webflow","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":120,"offset":1997},"end":{"line":24,"column":127,"offset":2004},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":119,"offset":1996},"end":{"line":24,"column":160,"offset":2037},"indent":[]}},{"type":"text","value":"等令你可輕易以低成本建立一個似模似樣的網站，讓客戶可以更容易在網上搜尋到你，並且增加對你公司的信任度。對於已經擁有網站的中小企而言，就需要完善網站的內容架構和在不同裝置上(例如電腦, 平板電腦和手機)的相融程度，讓客戶願意在網站上停留更久，令公司在搜尋器上突圍而出，增加網站自然流量。","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":160,"offset":2037},"end":{"line":24,"column":302,"offset":2179},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1,"offset":1878},"end":{"line":24,"column":302,"offset":2179},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"網上直播 Live","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":3,"offset":2183},"end":{"line":26,"column":12,"offset":2192},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1,"offset":2181},"end":{"line":26,"column":14,"offset":2194},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"現時網上直播大為流行，而直播的點播率和轉換率也比其他方面的宣傳(例如圖片和預先錄製影片)的收看率更高。中小企業可利用Facebook 和 Instagram 等社交平台進行直播，增加和客戶的互動，直播後更可將影片轉換成廣告，進行追蹤式再行銷廣告，針對看過直播的客戶，刺激他們的消費意欲，增加產品和服務的銷售。","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1,"offset":2195},"end":{"line":27,"column":155,"offset":2349},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":1,"offset":2195},"end":{"line":27,"column":155,"offset":2349},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"客戶網上評論 Customer Reviews","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":3,"offset":2353},"end":{"line":29,"column":26,"offset":2376},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1,"offset":2351},"end":{"line":29,"column":28,"offset":2378},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"客戶的口碑遠勝過你的千言萬語。客戶使用過你的服務或者產品，用他們的第一身體驗來評價產品更有說服力。中小企業和初創公司可鼓勵客戶在網上，例如Google My Business 、Facebook Page 的Review上留言或為產品服務進行評分，或是推薦產品或服務，吸引潛在的客戶使用公司的產品服務。中小企應積極回應客戶的評論和留言，藉此提升客戶的忠誠度。","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1,"offset":2379},"end":{"line":30,"column":180,"offset":2558},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1,"offset":2379},"end":{"line":30,"column":180,"offset":2558},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"中小企和初創公司只要稍微加點創意和花點心思，利用以上的網上低成本方法來推廣生意，一樣可以成功突圍而出，令業務蒸蒸日上！","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1,"offset":2560},"end":{"line":32,"column":60,"offset":2619},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1,"offset":2560},"end":{"line":32,"column":60,"offset":2619},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":32,"column":60,"offset":2619}}}}